Businesses need a single platform where all customer issues can be logged, tracked, and monitored in real time. This avoids scattered communication through emails, calls, or chats.
Manual ticket distribution is time-consuming and often unfair. An automated system ensures tickets are assigned to the right agent based on priority and availability.
